{"text_id":197359,"tokens":["The"," spin"," of"," carriers"," in"," semiconductor"," structures"," has"," recently"," attracted"," a"," lot"," of"," interest"," due"," to"," the"," possibility"," to"," generate"," and"," manipulate"," spin","-","polarized"," currents"," with"," the"," use"," of"," either"," magnetic"," or"," non","-","magnetic"," structures","."," The"," low","-","dimension","ality"," of"," semiconductor"," systems",","," such"," as"," two","-","dimensional"," electron"," and"," hole"," gases"," (","2","DEG"," and"," ","2","DH","G",","," respectively","),"," plays"," a"," crucial"," role"," in"," spin","-","related"," phenomena","."," Despite"," many"," achievements"," in"," the"," study"," of"," electron"," systems",","," the"," role"," of"," the"," Lut","tinger"," term"," in"," the"," Kane"," model"," of"," the"," ","2","DH","G"," has"," not"," been"," fully"," explored","."," We"," present"," a"," theoretical"," study"," of"," the"," resonant"," spin"," polarization"," in"," a"," ","2","DH","G"," with"," the"," Lut","tinger"," term",","," structural"," inversion"," asymmetry"," and"," Ze","eman"," splitting","."," We"," show"," that"," the"," resonant"," spin"," polarization"," excited"," by"," circular","ly"," polarized"," light"," depends"," on"," the"," light"," frequency"," and"," has"," multiple"," peaks",","," which"," are"," related"," to"," the"," light","-","induced"," modification"," of"," the"," Lut","tinger"," term","."," The"," presented"," results"," could"," be"," useful"," for"," the"," further"," experimental"," studies"," of"," spin","-","related"," phenomena"," in"," ","2","DH","G"," systems","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"dolly","label":1}